OL,3,CTartan Army arrive in force in Boston
OL,4,Cahead of Scotland's first World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FThe Tartan Army has arrived in force
OL,8,Fin Boston as fans kick off
OL,9,Fcelebrations ahead of Scotland's first
OL,10,FWorld Cup match in 28 years.
OL,12,FFirst Minister John Swinney, actor
OL,13,FGerard Butler and singer Clare Grogan
OL,14,Fare among the famous figures who have
OL,15,Fmade the trip to Massachusetts, ready
OL,16,Ffor the team's first fixture against
OL,17,FHaiti on Saturday at 9pm local time `
OL,18,F2am BST.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
