FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781408877
OL,3,CTartan Army arrive in force in Boston
OL,4,Cahead of Scotland's first World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FThey were among guests who were
OL,8,Fgreeted by a piper as they arrived at
OL,9,Fa Scottish Night in Boston Dinner and
OL,10,FGala Event at the Royale in Boston.
OL,12,FButler, star of the movie 300, wore a
OL,13,Fkilt and football shirt and gave a
OL,14,Fthumbs up as he arrived at the event
OL,15,Fheld in aid of Street Soccer Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781408877
OL,3,CTartan Army arrive in force in Boston
OL,4,Cahead of Scotland's first World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FAlso seen arriving at the gala, were
OL,8,FBaby Reindeer creator Richard Gadd,
OL,9,Falso sporting a kilt, actors Martin
OL,10,FCompston and Tony Curran, former
OL,11,Ffootballers James McFadden and Darren
OL,12,FFletcher and broadcaster Gordon Smart.
OL,14,FArriving in a tartan-covered car was
OL,15,FMike Mulraney, the president of the
OL,16,FScottish Football Association, and
OL,17,FNeil Doncaster, chief executive of the
OL,18,FScottish Premier League. Former rugby
OL,19,Funion player Gregor Townsend also
OL,20,Fattended the event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781408877
OL,3,CTartan Army arrive in force in Boston
OL,4,Cahead of Scotland's first World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FBars in the city were flooded with
OL,8,Fblue, tartan and the Saltire including
OL,9,Fthe Scotland House at the Anchor Bar,
OL,10,Fwhere a water fountain was filled with
OL,11,Ffoam as fans began their celebrations.
OL,13,FA group of fans at the Scottish pub
OL,14,FThe Haven unveiled a massive flag with
OL,15,Fthe slogan "The Party's Back".
OL,17,FOne fan said: "I'm absolutely buzzing
OL,18,Ffor it, it's been six months of
OL,19,Fwaiting."
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@]O]yD@OOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
