OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781408877
OL,3,CTartan Army arrive in force in Boston
OL,4,Cahead of Scotland's first World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FAnother said: "I've been saving up for
OL,8,Fmonths and months to be here."
OL,10,FCharity fundraiser Craig Ferguson was
OL,11,Fmet with cheers as he completed a
OL,12,F3,000-mile kilted charity walk across
OL,13,Fthe United States in aid of Scottish
OL,14,FAction for Mental Health (SAMH).
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
