FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781408877
OL,3,CTartan Army arrive in force in Boston
OL,4,Cahead of Scotland's first World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FThe 22-year-old managed to complete
OL,8,Fthe hike, which he started in February
OL,9,Fin Los Angeles, with a day to spare
OL,10,Fand was met by local pipers at Boston
OL,11,FCommon on Friday.
OL,13,FThere he was also greeted by crowds of
OL,14,Fsupporters, members of the Tartan Army
OL,15,Fand Scottish expats, some waving
OL,16,FScotland flags as they cheered and
OL,17,Fchanted "no Scotland, no party".
OL,19,FMr Ferguson afterwards said the
OL,20,Freception was "everything (he) could
OL,21,Fhave dreamed of".
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@_O]|D@OOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
