OL,3,CTartan Army arrive in force in Boston
OL,4,Cahead of Scotland's first World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FShortly before finishing the walk Mr
OL,8,FFerguson, who is from Paisley,
OL,9,FRenfrewshire, also learned the
OL,10,FScottish Government had made a
OL,11,F#400,000 donation to his walk ` and he
OL,12,Fhas now reached his #1 million
OL,13,Ffundraising target.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
